flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Receive User Question"]
    B --> C["Load Document Store<br/>(summaries + content)"]
    C --> D["Display Document<br/>Summaries to Agent"]
    D --> E{"Has enough<br/>context?"}
    E -->|No| F["Agent Selects<br/>Next Document"]
    F --> G["Retrieve Full<br/>Document Content"]
    G --> H["Accumulate Context<br/>from Document"]
    H --> E
    E -->|Yes| I["Generate Final Answer<br/>from Accumulated Context"]
    I --> J([End])